---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Recverse — AI & IT Services für moderne Unternehmen"
  description="Recverse liefert KI-MVPs, IT-Projektmanagement und moderne Web-Präsenzen. Enterprise-Look, schlanke Umsetzung, klare Resultate."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-left card">
          <div class="pill"><span class="dot"></span> Enterprise-Level Umsetzung ohne Overhead</div>

          <h1 style="margin-top:14px; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', Inter, system-ui;">
            KI & IT-Delivery, die Vertrauen schafft — und Resultate liefert.
          </h1>

          <p class="hero-lead">
            Recverse unterstützt KMUs auf dem Weg zur Moderne: von KI-PoC/MVP über Projektmanagement bis zur performanten Web-Präsenz.
            Klarer Scope. Sauberer Code. Saubere Übergabe.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact">Projekt anfragen</a>
            <a class="btn" href="/services">Scope-Check</a>
          </div>

          <div class="trust-row" aria-label="Trust Signals">
            <div class="trust-item">
              <strong>Governance-light</strong>
              <span>Risiken sichtbar, Entscheidungen schnell</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-item">
              <strong>Delivery-Fokus</strong>
              <span>MVP-fähig, wartbar, deploybar</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-item">
              <strong>B2B-Ready</strong>
              <span>Saubere Doku & Übergabe</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-right card" aria-label="Hero Visual Panel">
          <div class="hero-panel">
            <div class="kicker">Was du erwarten kannst</div>
            <h3 style="margin-top:6px;">Modernisierung, die nicht nach „Spielerei“ aussieht.</h3>

            <div class="bullets">
              <div class="bullet">
                <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                    <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8Z" stroke="rgb(244 246 255)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <strong>KI-PoC → MVP</strong>
                  <span>Nutzen, Datenfluss, Risiken, Demo – in einem lieferbaren Scope.</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="bullet">
                <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                    <path d="M5 20V4m0 0h6a3 3 0 0 1 0 6H5m0 0h10a3 3 0 0 1 0 6H5" stroke="rgb(244 246 255)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Transformation & IT PM</strong>
                  <span>Backlog, Stakeholder, Cutover/Go-Live – ohne unnötige Rituale.</span>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="bullet">
                <div class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                    <path d="M12 2 20 6v6c0 5-3.5 9.5-8 10-4.5-.5-8-5-8-10V6l8-4Z" stroke="rgb(244 246 255)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Trust & Qualität</strong>
                  <span>Performance-first, A11y-Basics, klare Struktur.</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top:10px;">
              <a class="btn ghost" href="/services">Leistungen ansehen</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      .hero{ padding: 64px 0 40px; position: relative; }
      .hero-grid{ display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:18px; align-items:start; }

      .hero-left{ padding: 22px; border-radius: var(--r-2xl); }
      .hero-lead{ margin-top: 16px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 62ch; }

      .hero-actions{ display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; margin-top: 18px; }

      .trust-row{ margin-top: 18px; display:grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap:10px; }
      .trust-item{
        padding: 14px;
        border-radius: var(--r-xl);
        border: 1px solid rgb(var(--border) / .25);
        background: rgb(var(--surface) / .20);
      }
      .trust-item strong{
        display:block;
        color: rgb(var(--text));
        font-weight: 750;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .trust-item span{ color: rgb(var(--muted)); font-size: 12px; }

      .hero-right{
        position: relative;
        padding: 22px;
        border-radius: var(--r-2xl);
        overflow: hidden;
        min-height: 280px;
      }
      .hero-right::before{
        content:"";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -80px;
        background:
          radial-gradient(420px 280px at 20% 25%, rgb(var(--accent) / .25), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(520px 340px at 80% 35%, rgb(var(--accent2) / .18), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(520px 420px at 45% 85%, rgb(255 255 255 / .05), transparent 60%);
        opacity: .95;
        animation: floatMesh 8s var(--ease) infinite alternate;
      }
      .hero-right::after{
        content:"";
        position:absolute;
        inset:0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgb(var(--bg) / 0.10), rgb(var(--bg) / 0.75));
        pointer-events:none;
      }
      @keyframes floatMesh{
        from { transform: translate3d(0,0,0) scale(1); }
        to   { transform: translate3d(16px,-10px,0) scale(1.03); }
      }

      .hero-panel{ position:relative; display:grid; gap: 12px; }
      .bullets{ display:grid; gap:10px; margin-top: 6px; }
      .bullet{
        display:grid;
        grid-template-columns: 26px 1fr;
        gap:10px;
        align-items:start;
        padding: 12px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        border: 1px solid rgb(var(--border) / .28);
        background: rgb(var(--surface2) / .22);
      }
      .icon{
        width: 26px;
        height: 26px;
        display:grid;
        place-items:center;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid rgb(var(--accent) / .28);
        background: rgb(var(--accent) / .10);
        box-shadow: 0 0 26px rgb(var(--accent) / .10);
      }
      .bullet strong{ display:block; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(var(--text)); font-weight: 750; }
      .bullet span{ display:block; margin-top:4px; color: rgb(var(--muted)); font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.55; }

      @media (min-width: 980px){
        .hero{ padding: 82px 0 56px; }
        .hero-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1.05fr .95fr; align-items: stretch; }
        .trust-row{ grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
        .hero-right{ min-height: 100%; }
      }

      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
        .hero-right::before{ animation: none; }
      }
    </style>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
